OL,3,CFashion retailer Shein finds two cases
OL,4,Cof child labour in supply change
OL,6,FFast-fashion retailer Shein found two
OL,7,Fcases of child labour at its suppliers
OL,8,Flast year and that some factories
OL,9,Ffailed to pay workers the minimum wage.
OL,11,FIn Shein's 2023 sustainability report,
OL,12,Fthe company said it stopped working
OL,13,Fwith manufacturers found to be
OL,14,Femploying children under 16 and
OL,15,Flaunched investigations into the
OL,16,Fmatter.
OL,18,F"From Q1 to Q3 2023, our SRS audits
OL,19,Funcovered two cases of child labour in
OL,20,Four supply chain," the company wrote.
