OL,3,CFashion retailer Shein finds two cases
OL,4,Cof child labour in supply change
OL,6,F"Upon discovering these violations,
OL,7,FSHEIN suspended orders from the
OL,8,Fcontract manufacturers and undertook
OL,9,Finvestigations.
OL,11,F"In accordance with the SRS Policy in
OL,12,Fplace at the time, errant suppliers
OL,13,Fwere given 30 days to remediate their
OL,14,Foffences."
OL,16,FShein said both cases were "swiftly
OL,17,Fresolved," with the underage workers'
OL,18,Fcontracts terminated, outstanding
OL,19,Fwages paid, and parents or legal
OL,20,Fguardians contacted.
