OL,3,CFashion retailer Shein finds two cases
OL,4,Cof child labour in supply change
OL,6,FAfter discovering the child labour
OL,7,Fcases, Shein tightened its supplier
OL,8,Fpolicy last October.
OL,10,FThe updated policy mandates that any
OL,11,Fsevere breaches, called "Immediate
OL,12,FTermination Violations," will lead to
OL,13,Fthe supplier's immediate dismissal.
OL,15,FShein wrote: "We remain vigilant in
OL,16,Fguarding against such violations going
OL,17,Fforward, and in line with current
OL,18,Fpolicies, will terminate any non-
OL,19,Fcompliant suppliers."
